citations.desc: Access and inspection of records and property; submission of itineraries.
citations.narrative:
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at 10:30am on
Thursday, 9 February 2023. The inspector was able to talk to the license via phone and the licensee stated that no one
was available for the inspection that day.
End Section
